     <td id="postings"><!-- ++++++++++++++BEGIN POSTINGS CONTENT++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ --> <img src="/eekoworld/images/exchange_det_water.gif" alt="How do you try to save water?"> <p>My family tries to save water by washing dishes by hand, and taking really quick showers! When you wash dishes by hand you save up a lot more water than you do when you use the dishwasher. We only use the dishwasher about once a month. Thats really goin' Green!! You can do it too if you really believe and try as hard as you can to save our planet.... remember, God put us on this planet to have fun, not to let Earth die out JUST because of not recycling enough!!! GO GREENS!!!!</p> <p>— Alex2015, Age 12</p>
      <hr> <p>After I wet my toothbrush I turn the water off.Then I turn it on and off.</p> <p>— mortyu, Age 8</p>
      <hr> <p>I save water by taking short showers and not deep baths.I would only take a bath if it was a doctors orders.I think everybody in the world should try to conserve water by taking short showers instead of baths and not leaving the water on while brushing your teeth!</p> <p>— lizzylizardz, Age 4</p>
      <hr> <p>I save water by catching rain water to use instead of electicity</p> <p>— Betaha, Age 9</p>
      <hr> <p>i save water by taking a shower and not a bath</p> <p>— horse230, Age 12</p>
      <hr> <p>Did you know you use about 15 gallons of water when you take a shower? so what i do is i put a plug in when im taking a shower so i use the same water to wash my feet as i did with my hair</p> <p>— Maia, Age 10</p>
      <hr> <p>By turning off the faucet when i brush my teeth and turning off any water i see that is on. Also we could save water by taking quick baths and showers as to not waist the water. I mean we only have so much to go around the earth.</p> <p>— tswells, Age 10</p>
      <hr> <p>My dad made a rain bucket to trap water so he can us it on the plants.</p> <p>— soapsoap, Age 12</p>
      <hr> <p>I save water in 3 ways#1 I close the water when I'm not using it in the shower,#2 I don't leave the water running when I'm brushing my teeth,and #3 we take the car to a car wash because it's better when you take it to the car wash,by hand you waste 5 times more water than in the car wash. Those r the 3 ways I save water I LOVE SAVING WATER IT'S FUN AND IT HELPS THE ENVIRONMENT!!!!!!!!</p> <p>— we2rf3, Age 10</p>
